Consumer will choose serialization class while decoding response at com.alibaba.dubbo.rpc.protocol.dubbo.DubboCodec::decodeBody(), it's the "header[2]" decides the serialization class, which is decided by provider.
Then I checked source code of encoding:
`Serialization serialization = getSerialization(channel);`
`
protected Serialization getSerialization(Channel channel) {
       return CodecSupport.getSerialization(channel.getUrl());
}
`
That url in channel will not be changed by configuration in <dubbo:service> or <dubbo:provider>

